18
00:00:49,016 --> 00:00:51,196
So I'm just gonna sort of boil this down

19
00:00:51,536 --> 00:00:57,658
and schemas have a very complicated relationship

20
00:00:57,779 --> 00:00:58,579
with human behavior.

21
00:00:59,722 --> 00:01:02,944
They are easily formed, easily activated, and never really turn off.

22
00:01:03,364 --> 00:01:07,106
And today we're going to explore the nature and the relevance of schemas to player behavior

23
00:01:07,847 --> 00:01:11,789
and how and why they function to drive player perceptions and how they guide decision making

24
